        </h2>
        <p>As a Salesforce CRM developer, you will be responsible for designing, creating, optimizing our Salesforce database functionality. You will be working closely with a web developer to create integrations between our website’s CMS and Salesforce. You will also be working autonomously on projects. The ideal candidate will provide insight, have a strong vision and architectural approach and be a pro-active problem solver. Strong organizational, prioritization and documentation skills. </p>

