          <li>Ability to build automated system for content management between the web app and Salesforce</li>
          <li>Customization (Apex triggers, classes and Visualforce pages)</li>
          <li>Configuration to include formulas, workflows, approval processes, custom objects and fields, sharing rules, page layouts, record types, permission sets, reports and dashboards</li>
          <li>Knowledge of relational databases and integrations</li>
          <li>Previous experience working with Salesforce.com partners</li>
          <li>Apply knowledge of all phases of the software development lifecycle – analysis, design, development, testing and production support</li>
