          <li>Deliver hands-on code and unit testing</li>
          <li>Analyze and resolve production issues</li>
          <li>Strong written and verbal communications are essential (including the ability to communicate clearly to non-technical team members)</li>
          <li>Continuous improvement attitude and ability to work with a team a must.</li>

